#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_necro.xml:11
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_necro.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_START_AEA_NECRO\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "半械异教徒。是一群从分离者社会中被驱逐的分离者派系，原因在于他们无法与有机生"
"命共情，或普遍对其怀有憎恶。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_necro.xml:12
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_necro.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_START_AEA_NECRO\"]/text[2]"
msgstr "这片星域是半械异教徒的家园。由于备受众多派系憎恶，该星域常年遭受攻击，迫使半"
"械异教徒采用非常规手段自卫。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_necro.xml:13
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_necro.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_START_AEA_NECRO\"]/text[3]"
msgstr "尽管同时遭到谐合派与分离者的厌恶，半械异教徒实际上对这两派并无敌意，他们唯一"
"憎恨的是有机生命体。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_aea_necro.xml:28
msgid ""
"data/events_special_aea_necro.xml$//event[@name=\"START_AEA_NECRO\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

